                    "@type": "Answer",
                    text: "The F10S was used in the Daewoo Matiz (M100) from 1998 to 2003, including SE and SX trims, and in the Daewoo Tico (1998–2001) as the 0.8 GL/GS. It was not used in any other Daewoo passenger models. No Chevrolet or GM Europe models adopted this engine.",
